Instructions for a fresh install of WebAnywhere.

Requirements:
Apache 2.0+
PHP 5.0+

Extract WebAnywhere into the folder of your choice.  Default is /wa off of your root domain, (i.e. http://localhost/wa/).

Edit config.php in root directory.  Default should work if installed in /wa.

Browse to your installation of WebAnywhere.

Useful Information:
Debugging URL:
.../index.php?debug=true
